        <h2>Guide: How to Check Your Result on the Univindia MGSU Portal</h2>
        <p>Checking your results on Univindia Maharaja Ganga Singh University is the most anticipated moment of the academic year. To ensure you can access your marksheet as soon as it's released, follow these steps:</p>
        <ol>
            <li><strong>Access the Official Portal:</strong> Visit the `univindia.net` website. Always verify the domain name to ensure you are on the university's authorized platform and not on an unofficial result aggregator.</li>
            <li><strong>Enter the Result Section:</strong> On the homepage, click on the link for 'Result Exam 2024-25'. This will open a new selection portal.</li>
            <li><strong>Identify Your Parameters:</strong> Select the Year, the Result Type (Main, Reval, or Supplementary), and your degree level (UG or PG).</li>
